The paper focuses on analyzing the development of sub-disciplines in computer science using social network analysis. The sub-disciplines are likely to fall under categories such as systems and control (cs.SY), social and information networks (cs.SI), databases (cs.DB), digital libraries (cs.DL), and software engineering (cs.SE).
